BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260309
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260310
SUMMARY:🌱 Direct Sow Day — Carrots, Peas, Spinach, Dill, Chives
DESCRIPTION:MORNING — Direct sow (windows close Mar 16):\n• Carrots (Danvers, Parisienne, Purple Dragon, Rainbow, Tendersweet) — Wildwood, 1/4" deep, rows 12" apart\n• Peas (Sugar Daddy) — Wildwood near trellis, 1" deep, 2" apart\n• Spinach (Bloomsdale) — Wildwood, 1/2" deep, 3" apart\n• Dill — herb spiral, surface sow, press lightly\n• Chives — herb spiral, 1/4" deep\n\nAFTERNOON:\n• Scatter poppy seeds on Bloomveil (Frosted Salmon, Purple Peony, Lilac PomPom, Jelly Beans). Press in, don't cover.\n• Start cantaloupe (Sierra Gold) indoors\n• Start cucumber (Mexican Sour Gherkin) indoors\n• Start watermelon (Bush Sugar Baby, Garden Leader Monster) indoors
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT0H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Garden: Direct Sow Day!
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

