BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261001
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261002
SUMMARY:🍂 October — Harvest, winterize, dahlia decision
DESCRIPTION:October priorities:\n• Harvest pumpkins, winter squash, sweet potatoes before frost\n• DAHLIA DECISION: dig tubers after first frost blackens foliage, OR mulch heavily in place (Zone 7b can go either way)\n• Cut back perennials that are done (leave seed heads for birds where possible)\n• Spread fallen leaves as mulch (don't bag!)\n• Last spinach sow (by Oct 7)\n• Clean and store tools\n• Note what worked and what didn't for next year
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT0H
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:October garden priorities
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT

